 nodrop status. On my main server (7th) there is a rather well-known incident where a pally lead a raid on Naggy, and made the rolls all/all (except for epic book). So a cleric got in on the roll and won the CoF (which has up to 50% haste depending on your level) ... and the raid leader gave it to him... needless to say, neither of those guys (cleric or the pally leading raid) won any popularity contests that day. It'd be like allowing melee classes other than bard/warrior to roll on the dragon scale drop, just so they can go quest a BP that isn't even tops in the game.<br><br>Need before greed is a good thing, it's just too bad more players don't follow that ideal.<br><br><br></p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
