ite dragon scale for your white dragon scale cloak (AC+10 Wis+9 Int+9 Cold Resist+25 Mana+75 )?-too bad I get first dibs on it for my bard epic. WOW a SMR just dropped? Neato that means I get it since I need it for my epic! Good job group! We just downed Phinny and that kedge robe that has some of the best stats on a robe in the game goes straight to me. Hands off Zlandicar&amp;#8217;s Talisman, do I CARE if it is one of the best neck items in the game? I need it for my ST key. That&amp;#8217;s how these posts are starting to sound. And to the person that wrote that they came across a druid trying to sell the MQ to their epic right in front of their eyes&amp;#8230;yes that was a tad on the greedy side. But all things said, It comes down to one thing-<br><br>Question: what is more important my epic or yours? <br>Answer&nbsp;&nbsp;: neither&amp;#8230;it is all relative. <br><br>To you my epic is just another item for me to help me do my job better while keeping me alive longer. To me your epic is just another item for you while helping you stay alive longer. Would you forego your rights to any of the above items so that I could get said item? Most likely not. <br><br>Last night I was escorting a friend of mine ( I &gt;coaxed&lt; him into the trap of EQ about a week ago heh) who is lvl 22 to SK to hunt at the tree house. While looking in my book for buffages for him I see him type: &amp;#8220;Whoa that&amp;#8217;s a cool looking horse&amp;#8221;. I respond by saying &amp;#8220;you don&amp;#8217;t have the new expansion so you cant see any horses&amp;#8221;. He said &amp;#8220;there it is, don&amp;#8217;t you see it?&amp;#8221;. I look up out of my book and there is Q, in all its rarespawn glory. So I drop my 49root on it, then assault it with Dementia (54 nuke) x2, Gasping Embrace (49 Dot), and Torment of Argli (56 Dot). Then sit to med. He was down in about 50 secs. I don&amp;#8217;t need the cloak since I have the lvl 51, SoL, componentless Levitation. I let h