 difference. The other stuff you mentioned has value, a levi cloak is just gravy. Now factor in the whole royal pain in the ass epic piece thing.<br><br>It's a nice thing for other classes to have, but mages have to get it if they want their epic. And then we have to give it up again to some filthy npc who probably doesn't appreciate the hell we had to go through to get it.<br><br>Now as I said, you do make a good point, but you're comparing different things. For any class other than mages, this hellish item is just icing.<br><br><br><br>Faelawen Starfyre, The Mad Mage of Povar</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
